title: Oklahoma U.S. Senate Results: James Lankford Wins

maintext:
Senator James Lankford won the U.S. Senate race in Oklahoma on Tuesday. Lankford is up by 43 points with all precincts reporting.
Below are detailed results for the race. View other Oklahoma election results on our full Oklahoma results page. See all races on our Senate map.
